  "prompt": "Where we can buy books online in Pune?",
  "response": "In Pune, you have several options to buy books online. Here are some popular platforms that you can explore:\n\n1. **Amazon India**: A major online retailer where you can find a wide selection of books in various genres, including new releases and bestsellers.\n\n2. **Flipkart**: Another leading e-commerce website in India offering a vast collection of books along with competitive discounts and deals.\n\n3. **Book Depository**: Known for its extensive catalog and free shipping worldwide, including to India.\n\n4. **Snapdeal**: Offers a range of books, often at discounted prices.\n\n5. **Crossword**: Although primarily known for its physical stores, Crossword also has an online presence where you can purchase books.\n\n6. **Infibeam**: An Indian online shopping site that offers a variety of books across different categories.\n\n7. **PustakKosh**: Specializes in renting and selling new and second-hand books, including academic textbooks.\n\n8. **Amazon Kindle Store**: If you prefer e-books, the Kindle Store is a great resource for purchasing and downloading electronic versions of your favorite books.\n\n9. **Local Bookstores' Online Platforms**: Many local bookstores in Pune have their own online portals or social media presence where you can place orders, such as Akshardhara and Crossword Pune.\n\nIt's always a good idea to compare prices and check for any delivery charges or additional fees when purchasing books online.",
